{"tid":19958,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"孽。麥浚龍","createTime":"2016-12-03T05:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T19:46:03.000Z","uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d03c3ecbd824b26423c5ce8e434071fd087fbc36","tid":19958,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主唱：麥浚龍<br />\n作曲：Vincent Chow<br />\n填詞：林夕<br />\n編曲：蔡德才@人山人海<br />\n<br />\n歌詞<br />\n<br />\n外面預備擲石頭<br />\n預備捕獵能互吻的禽獸<br />\n小畜牲 劊子手 哪個更自由<br />\n大地盡是菜市口<br />\n犯下罪狀是下流<br />\n剩下石像沈默援手<br />\n守清規 守不到一线青天<br />\n這罪孽誰庇佑<br />\n為何連神佛都低下頭<br />\n由凡人來滅我活口<br />\n碰見你 看見愛 看見我<br />\n生與死 都不枉 沾滿這雙手<br />\n等一等 低首親吻你後<br />\n懲罰我 誰顫抖 我仰首<br />\n這剎那 我先聽到心跳是什麼感受<br />\n能用你 脈搏聲 做伴奏 像踏浪 送扁舟"},{"pid":"63be8c74b85b1535505a37e0fac38980f88cfc93","tid":19958,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"蔡德才嘅編曲真係好正！"},{"pid":"3d562a176d2179bebca1c237d73de6c99612be73","tid":19958,"uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"蔡德才編曲一流，尾段人聲合唱、同最尾唱罪咎，好正！"},{"pid":"5cb9c45ff3d503f53af7b72d8508965de8a3f5af","tid":19958,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T00:45:00.000Z","msg":"有錢真好<br />\n柒頭一個都可以有正歌唱"},{"pid":"bddfb852f424b784790896f3f3b17e10ddd7bf90","tid":19958,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢真好<br />\n柒頭一個都可以有正歌唱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係事實，有錢，可以唔使理賺唔賺錢"},{"pid":"b4c0967b0502270207c3b713b959b5aad0444228","tid":19958,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蔡德才編曲一流，尾段人聲合唱、同最尾唱罪咎，好正！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a31000a01d188c5470ad19ccac2b66250b3f86","tid